replies.body:
I have loved watching this progress via your Twitter updates... So pretty!
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}} 

I do think her feet/lower legs are a bit lacking, maybe even just a touch of jewelry or a ribbon would balance it a bit more. Thematically, I think the use of hair in place of her plants really works out well. I could easily see this as a great addition to the Blood Moon line.
